---
/**
 * PairDish.com - Privacy Policy
 *
 * Our commitment to protecting your privacy.
 */

import BaseLayout from '../components/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "January 3, 2026";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="PairDish Privacy Policy - Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our culinary tools."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-12 md:py-16 overflow-hidden bg-[var(--color-cream)]">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="badge badge-wine mb-4">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="text-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-4">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)]">
          Last updated: {lastUpdated}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">

        <div class="bg-[var(--color-cream)] rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
          <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] m-0">
            <strong class="text-[var(--text-primary)]">Summary:</strong> We respect your privacy.
            PairDish is designed to work without requiring personal data. We don't sell your information,
            and we only collect minimal analytics to improve our tools.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-display text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">
          1. Information We Collect
        </h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-6 mb-3">
          Information You Provide
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          PairDish tools are designed to work without requiring you to create an account or provide personal information.
          Any data you enter into our tools (such as ingredients, recipe quantities, or guest counts) is processed
          locally in your browser and is not stored on our servers.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-6 mb-3">
          Automatically Collected Information
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          Like most websites, we automatically collect certain information when you visit PairDish:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Operating system</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on each page</li>
          <li>Referring website (how you found us)</li>
          <li>General geographic location (country/region level only)</li>
          <li>Device type (mobile, desktop, tablet)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          This information is collected through privacy-respecting analytics and is used solely to understand
          how our tools are used and how we can improve them.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">
          2. How We Use Your Information
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          We use the automatically collected information to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Understand which tools are most popular and useful</li>
          <li>Identify and fix technical issues</li>
          <li>Improve the user experience and design of our website</li>
          <li>Make informed decisions about new features and tools</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-display text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">
          3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          PairDish uses minimal cookies necessary for the website to function properly. We may use:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Required for basic website functionality</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Help us understand how visitors interact with our site</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          You can control cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies may affect
          some functionality of our tools.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">
          4. Data Sharing and Disclosure
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          <strong>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          We may share aggregated, anonymized data (such as "50% of our users access the site on mobile")
          for analytical purposes, but this data cannot be used to identify individual users.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          We may disclose information if required by law or if we believe such action is necessary to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
          <li>Protect and defend our rights or property</li>
          <li>Prevent fraud or abuse of our services</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-display text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">
          5. Data Security
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          We take reasonable measures to protect the information we collect. Our website uses HTTPS
          encryption to secure data transmitted between your browser and our servers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          However, no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.
          While we strive to protect your information, we cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">
          6. Third-Party Services
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          PairDish is hosted on Cloudflare Workers and may use the following third-party services:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> For website hosting, security, and performance optimization</li>
          <li><strong>Google Fonts:</strong> For typography (loaded with privacy-preserving settings)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          These services have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">
          7. Children's Privacy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          PairDish is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect personal information
          from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information,
          please contact us and we will delete it promptly.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">
          8. Your Rights
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          Depending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding your personal information:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Right to access the information we have about you</li>
          <li>Right to request deletion of your information</li>
          <li>Right to opt out of analytics tracking</li>
          <li>Right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          Since we collect minimal data and don't require accounts, there is typically little to no
          personal data associated with individual users.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">
          9. Changes to This Policy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by
          posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-display text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] mt-8 mb-4">
          10. Contact Us
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-4">
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-[var(--color-cream)] rounded-xl p-6">
          <p class="text-[var(--text-primary)] font-semibold m-0 mb-2">PairDish</p>
          <p class="text-[var(--text-secondary)] m-0">
            Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@pairdish.com" class="text-[var(--color-wine)] hover:underline">privacy@pairdish.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-cream-dark);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
